  "remarks": "\nBrigadier General Ali Reza Balali is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 through his role as Senior Adviser to the Chief of the Islamic Revolutionary Guards Corps Aerospace Force (IRGC AF) he is or has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty, or independence of Ukraine. \n",
